      <title>美联储九月降息预期推动美国国债月末上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示最早可能在 9 月降息后，美国国债价格上涨。此次上涨标志着美国债券连续第三个月上涨，创下三年来最长的上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-31/treasuries-rally-into-fed-meeting-with-a-september-cut-at-stake</guid>
